Class MyMap

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.wmich.cs3310.hw3.Kubath.application.MyMap

  • public class MyMap
extends java.lang.Object
    MyMap is used to change the order of the alphabet. This allows sorts to sort as normal, but the values are changed based on the HashMap.

    Jonah Kubath

        public MyMap(java.lang.String name)
        Overloaded constructor for MyMap. Takes the value of name. Sets the first values to be sorted as the characters in the name. The final characters are alphabetical skipping the letters already used in the name.
